reviews: Not as advertised. Cheap case, not happy at all, but I will keep it because is cheap.

I got the backpack and I am happy with it. Shipment was on time. The only thing is that the color of the backpack is not dark blue as it shows in the picture. The color was light blu which I am a bit disappointed. However, I like the size of it and it is really good for day to day use.
Nothing to complain about it, like it.
I broke after 2 days of use

review_title: Great product but sent new watch with the same issue.
